description:
Looking for an error free reverse LED for your Euro Tails, look no further. We have tested and created a solution. This kit has everything you will need to create an error free reverse LED for your Euro Tails. These work with the -Euro Replica Taillights -Ed's Euro Taillights -OEM Euro Taillights You will need to use the resistors that are given in the kit and the t-taps to connect your wires to the resistor. We will have a DIY coming out soon. Please choose on the bottom for either 1 or 2 kits *You only need 1 KIT if you have 1 Reverse Light, if you have 2 reverse Lights please choose the 2 Kit option! *Resistors come with 3M Double sided tape for easy installation, this will eliminate the need to drill anything in your taillights. 1 Kit includes: 1 Error Canceler (Resistor) 2 T-taps 1 Bright CREE LEDs 2 Kits includes: 2 Error Cancelers (Resistors). 4 T-taps. 2 Bright CREE LEDs
----------DIY----------
 Click here for MK6 Euro Tail Reverse LED Kit Install DIY Video
----------DIY----------
As you will see from the video, this takes about all of 2 minutes to install: Step 1: Using the 3m double sided tape that comes already attached on our resistor, tape the gold resistor on the inside of the brake taillights. Step 2: Using the red T-tap, place the YELLOW Reverse Wire in the t-tap and the RED resistor wire next to it in the t-tap. Press down with a pair of pliers to create the connection and snap the t-tap in place to secure the connection. Step 3: Do the same as step2 but with the THIN BROWN (not thicker of the two wires) wire from the reverse light and the RED wire from the resistor. Press down with a pair of pliers to create the connection and snap the t-tap in place to secure the connection. Step 4: Enjoy your bright crisp white CREE euro tail reverse LEDs!
